 />\n有 ai 揸緊飛機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未有ai 不過有無人戰機好耐啦</blockquote><br />\n雖然而家已經算係AI揸緊，但係AI只係負責航程，其他都係由機師負責，例如高度所以takeoff 一定要人手，就算退一萬步Ai 可以控制成架機，但係機師唔只要控制架機仲有其他工作 例如有人在半空心臟病發機師都有野做揾醫生 call控制搭 仲有如個佢死左機師要負責接遺囑 同安置條屍 依啲野ai都做唔到</blockquote><br />\n有錯請屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該話AI係做到上述嘅嘢，只不過人類只相信人類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得就算AI取代到機師, 都一定要有個機長喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係喺個叫天不應叫地不聞嘅地方冇個話事人喺度真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494b49322cbf36769d3087cd79c5899dea573934","tid":388284,"uid":50021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:49:31.000Z","msg":"看更"},{"pid":"4ac40bf58ae7ba834efbbe1416e5311c59bdf97c","tid":388284,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>機師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔認同，畢竟而家已經算係AI揸緊，一定有人覺得要有個Last resort。</blockquote><br />\nNo offence 你覺得人既reliability 高過電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人製造嘅意外多過機械，但重點不在於此，然後，我覺得有AI雖然機師唔會消失，但係一定會裁員。</blockquote><br />\n有 ai 揸緊飛機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動導航計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連ai係比乜都唔知就係度懶係討論咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee78f11c145b2a4b8c1ee1612a15c753f45f0e4","tid":388284,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:54:35.000Z"